commits.commitMessage:
Enforce using local legato/toolchain/map for HL78.

Originally the makefile would pick up the legato root and toolchain
from the environment if they were defined there. Since toolchain &
legato are included in the hl78 product manifest, they should always
be present so don't allow overriding.

Resolves: LE-8178
Change-Id: Ib8921d3429b964bd508c644346edaecdb4642a55
commits.subject: Enforce using local legato/toolchain/map for HL78.

comments.message: Should verify that required variables (MIPS_ELF_ROOT) are set.
Why TOOLCHAIN_ROOT here but MIPS_ELF_ROOT elsewhere?
Patch Set 2: Patch Set 1 was rebased
Change has been successfully merged by Keith Dunwoody

commits.commitMessage:
Rename TARGET to TARGET_ARCH

This prevents conflict with Legato TARGET variable and allows toolchainDefs.mk
to be included directly with Legato makefiles.

Resolves: LE-7935
Change-Id: Ia347ba92ff546b410ff73ea281595b755c5aa1e2
commits.subject: Rename TARGET to TARGET_ARCH
